title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Works Of Art, Collectors' Pieces & Antiques
description: Imports Intra Eu - Works Of Art, Collectors' Pieces & Antiques in the United Kingdom increased to 89.67 GBP Million in September from 42.13 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Works Of Art, Collectors' Piece in the United Kingdom averaged 21.98 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 157.67 GBP Million in November of 2015 and a record low of 0.82 GBP Million in August of 1996.
